Battera::

She looked at CyberShark. "UH, I was wondering. Since you got 
upgraded, wold it be possable for me to get some upgrades too? 
Nothing big. But, I could use some more fire power. All I had as a 
weapon when I was flying in that battle was my optic lazars. I was 
just wondering....Oh, never mind. It's stupid." She turned and walked 
down the hall.
